### Route to save a person
POST http://localhost:8080/api/people HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João",
  "idade": 25,
  "email": "fulano@gmail.com",
  "sobrenome": "Silva"
}

### Route to pick up all the people
GET http://localhost:8080/api/people HTTP/2
Content-Type: application/json

### Route to update a person by id
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/people/{{id}}} HTTP/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João",
  "idade": 25,
  "email": "teu_cu@gmail.com",
  "sobrenome": "Silva"
}

### Route to find a person by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/people/{{id}}} HTTP/2
Content-Type: application/json

### Route to delete a person by id
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/people/{{id}}} HTTP/2
Content-Type: application/json